bug.short_desc: mediawriter offers previous version of workstation by default
bug.cf_doc_type: If docs needed, set a value

long_desc.thetext:
mediawriter-4.0.4-0
When Fedora 25 was released, and releases.json was updated to offer it, mediawriter will select the Fedora 24 version by default. You can click to change the version (and you will see Fedora 25 is actually selected there). You will have to select Fedora 24, then click version again and select Fedora 25.
It should just offer Fedora 25 by default.
